Class GCellUuid

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.gcell.ibeacon.gcellbeaconscanlibrary.GCellUuid

  • public class GCellUuid
extends java.lang.Object

    Represents a Proximity UUID

    The GCellUuid Class

    The GCellUuid class represents a iBeacon proximity UUID (universally unique identifier), which is a 128-bit value that uniquely identifies one or more beacons as a certain type or from a certain organization or project. This class stores the UUID and allows it to be displayed and formatted in a number of ways. It will also tst to see if a UUID is the default GCell UUID
